name: NSKeyedUnarchiver
desc: A decoder that restores data from an archive referenced by keys.

items.name: unarchiveTopLevelObjectWithData
items.desc: Decodes a previously-archived object graph, and returns the root object.

items.name: unarchivedObject<DecodedObjectType>
items.desc: Decodes a previously-archived object graph, and returns the root object as the specified type.

items.name: unarchivedObject
items.desc: Decodes a previously-archived object graph, returning the root object as one of the specified classes.

items.name: requiresSecureCoding
items.desc: Indicates whether the receiver requires all unarchived classes to conform to NSSecureCoding.

items.name: unarchiveObject
items.desc: Decodes and returns the object graph previously encoded by NSKeyedArchiver and stored in a given NSData object.

items.name: unarchiveObject
items.desc: Decodes and returns the object graph previously encoded by NSKeyedArchiver written to the file at a given path.

items.name: containsValue
items.desc: Returns a Boolean value that indicates whether the archive contains a value for a given key within the current decoding scope.

items.name: decodeDecodable<T>
items.desc: Decodes a decodable value associated with a given key.

items.name: decodeTopLevelDecodable<T>
items.desc: Decodes a top-level decodable value associated with a given key.

items.name: decodeBool
items.desc: Decodes a Boolean value associated with a given key.

items.name: decodeBytes
items.desc: Decodes a stream of bytes associated with a given key.

items.name: decodeDouble
items.desc: Decodes a double-precision floating-point value associated with a given key.

items.name: decodeFloat
items.desc: Decodes a single-precision floating-point value associated with a given key.

items.name: decodeInt32
items.desc: Decodes a 32-bit integer value associated with a given key.

items.name: decodeInt64
items.desc: Decodes a 64-bit integer value associated with a given key.

items.name: decodeObject
items.desc: Decodes and returns an object associated with a given key.

items.name: finishDecoding
items.desc: Tells the receiver that you are finished decoding objects.

items.name: decodingFailurePolicy
items.desc: The action to take when this unarchiver fails to decode an entry.

items.name: delegate
items.desc: The receiverâ€™s delegate.

items.name: setClass
items.desc: Sets a global translation mapping to decode objects encoded with a given class name as instances of a given class instead.

items.name: class
items.desc: Returns the class from which this unarchiver instantiates an encoded object with a given class name.

items.name: setClass
items.desc: Sets a translation mapping on this unarchiver to decode objects encoded with a given class name as instances of a given class instead.

items.name: class
items.desc: Returns the class from which this unarchiver instantiates an encoded object with a given class name.
